snippet.description:

Led by Jayson Tatum's record-setting performance (55 points, 10 rebounds, 6 assists), Team Giannis defeats Team LeBron, 184-175.  Donovan Mitchell (40 points, 10 assists) and Damian Lillard (26 points, 4 assists, 8 3PM) added a combined 66 points in the victory.  Joel Embiid (32 points, 6 rebounds) and Kyrie Irving (32 points, 15 assists) added a combined 64 points for Team LeBron in the losing effort.
